}

}

question: In what climate does Allergy to substance (finding) occur in most?

PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral>

PREFIX loinc: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#loinc:LOINC>

SELECT ?climate
WHERE {
  ?allergy a Allergy .
  ?allergy Allergy#code snomed:SNOMED-CT .
  ?patient Patient#address ?address .
  ?address Patient#city ?city .
  ?city Patient#state ?state .
  ?state Patient#climate ?climate .
  ?allergy Allergy#patient ?patient .
}

ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?allergy))
